# Commit message template
# 
# Format: <type>: <subject>
# 
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
# 
# Example:
# feat: add user authentication
# 
# - Implemented JWT-based auth
# - Added login/logout endpoints
# - Updated user schema
# 
